{"tid":543590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"GOAL! 疑踩油當brake　警車褪後突加速撞七人車","createTime":"2018-01-28T15:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T03:39:22.000Z","uid":5195,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"093c818cdd55b444b9e65f0c4e9c9e2c3cdcef94","tid":543590,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:55:04.000Z","msg":"【被質疑踩油當brake　警車褪後突加速撞七人車】有片<br />\n<br />\n今日（1月28日）晚上，網上流傳一條車cam片段，見到一輛警車倒車時，竟撞向一輛黑色七人車。<br />\n<br />\n根據車cam片段顯示，時間為今日晚上7時39分，地點為土瓜灣美善同道與美善同里交界。片段所見，當時警車開始慢慢褪車，但之後卻見突然加速，撞向七人車側，駕車的警員隨即急急下車了解。<br />\n<br />\n片段上載到「馬路的事討論區」之後，有網民留言懷疑是「踩油當brake」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/833142083471222/permalink/1682597041859051/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F833142083471222%2Fpermalink%2F1682597041859051%2F&d=9ZLfab60MJFe0WuPRHKg0C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=4163f936\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/833142083471222/permalink/1682597041859051/</a>"},{"pid":"49eae44a5438ef3d3e6a03a2533e90ea5d1729d2","tid":543590,"uid":29093,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:56:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仆街  你襲警 ?  屌你老母 ! </span></span>"},{"pid":"c578df13ffff790caf99f0341eda436bc0d51b2b","tid":543590,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:57:38.000Z","msg":"得分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a95dcfbdb5befc2298fe80c3384ecaa764304f","tid":543590,"uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/023501_8e40a78f57615a0e932040392fff5991.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F023501_8e40a78f57615a0e932040392fff5991.jpg&h=1ec8e9d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"255ab8a86c9805b63a66e4